Taiwan Says Nuclear Power Is Necessary Choice, Evening News Says

-- B y   Y u - h u a y   S u n
-- 
2011-03-28T08:36:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/taiwan-says-nuclear-power-is-necessary-choice-evening-news-says.html
Nuclear power will remain a
necessary choice for Taiwan in the coming decades to ensure
stable and affordable energy supply, the United Evening News
reported today, citing Minister of Economic Affairs Shih Yen-
shiang.                                         Click here for web link  To contact the reporter on this story:
